# Music Genre Classification

## A machine learning project that classifies music into 10 genres using extracted audio features from the GTZAN dataset.

# Overview

## This project explores whether measurable audio characteristics can accurately predict a song's genre. 
Three classification models are compared: Logistic Regression, Random Forest, and Support Vector Machine(SVM),
with the SVM achieving the best results at 91.3% test accuracy.

# Genres Classified

## Blues, Classical, Country, Disco, Hip-Hop, Jazz, Metal, Pop, Reggae, Rock


